  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this uncontrolled, non-randomized, prospective, local post-marketed surveillance study,
      data are obtained on safety and efficacy of LEVITRA® in routine treatment of erectile
      dysfunction. The general objectives are to evaluate the product safety (primarily by
      recording adverse events), efficacy and patient acceptance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
